public class ParallelFlow

A multiple successor flow which creates a new work thread per outgoing branch. Meets the Parallel Split pattern (WFP2)

next

public void next(WorkThread wThread)
Description copied from class: BasicFlow
Requests this flow successor(s) to continue the execution. This method is invoked after all the tasks associated to this flow has been successfully carried out. Assigns this flow as the last flow visited by the work thread.

Overrides:
next in class BasicFlow
Parameters:
